<div class="description">
    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>Zend_Validate_Hostname should add support for reg-names.
See <a href="http://tools.ietf.org/html/rfc3986#section-3.2.2">http://tools.ietf.org/html/rfc3986#section-3.2.2</a> for detials.</p>

<p>This is basically a name composed of most unreserved characters, incl. underscores, tildas etc. You can also use the same type of host names in /etc/hosts for example. It's way more permissive than DNS.</p>

<p>This detection should be off per default</p>

